{"type": "article", "id": 21604, "title": "alphabet-shaped chairs  by Jean Paul Gaultier", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-01T01:00:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 17, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606161355oX7cjOIHNlg0TUDr.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">法国家具品牌 Tabisso 曾根据英文字母和阿拉伯数字等符号设计了一系列椅子，这些常见的符号都经过了夸张和变形，非常有趣。在巴黎家博会上，法国设计师 Jean Paul Gaultier 带来的 JPG 三个字母椅子却有一种生锈的感觉，他使用了人工皮革，红绿纹路的图案让它极具工业感，脱离了儿童式的活泼有趣，更能受到年轻人的认可。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606161352iYh4oILH3dJRDByn.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.19017094\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061613528Kc6EJLeh7f5z0kH.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606161353f8UDmj9aTyLnWCFc.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606161354fSa75GKIveEtozcO.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71047009\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606161354UBpeQhlrwFfVKqGJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71688034\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div>\n\n\n"}